  "lore": {
    "key": "Tbl_Unit_Desc_143",
    "english": "Demon, a member of the onis. Adjusting to the culture and life in the human world, they serve as mercenaries in the underworld. Wearing clothes and acting like a Sengoku Era samurai in Japan, they use their bow with superhuman focus, sniping and assassinating a target from long range.",
